    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>I agree with Petar Ivanov but it is best if we implement in following way:</p>\n\n<pre><code>public String replace(String str, int index, char replace){     \n    if(str==null){\n        return str;\n    }else if(index&lt;0 || index&gt;=str.length()){\n        return str;\n    }\n    char[] chars = str.toCharArray();\n    chars[index] = replace;\n    return String.valueOf(chars);       \n}\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 374470,
      "reputation" : 30383,
      "user_id" : 724689,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "accept_rate" : 84,
      "profile_image" : "https://i.sstatic.net/N2ebu.jpg?s=256",
      "display_name" : "kazinix",
      "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/users/724689/kazinix"
    },
    "is_accepted" : false,
