      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "I haven&#39;t downvoted your answer but I must admit I have a problem with the term &quot;overwrite&quot; (though I think we agree on the concept behind). The object itself remains unchanged. You just make your variable reference another object. By the way it you be interesting to mention that you create at least four String instances in your example."
